### Criar solicitação de registro
POST http://localhost:3000/user/registration/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "example-name",
  "email": "name@example.com",
  "password": "p123456",
  "profession": "DESENVOLVEDOR",
  "bio": "Backend developer"
}

### Listar solicitações de registro (admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/user/registration/requests?status=PENDING&page=1&perPage=10
Content-Type: application/json
admin-id: admin-uuid-here

### Aprovar solicitação de registro (admin)
POST http://localhost:3000/user/registration/:id/approve
Content-Type: application/json
admin-id: admin-uuid-here

### Rejeitar solicitação de registro (admin)
POST http://localhost:3000/user/registration/:id/reject
Content-Type: application/json
admin-id: admin-uuid-here

{
  "reason": "Perfil não atende aos requisitos"
}

